beer.beer_description: This easy drinking lager was specially crafted to honour friendships and celebrate achievements – paying homage to a time where telling stories, cheers and post-match banter was an important tradition. Keepers Lager is crafted using sun-dried malt and infused with citrus Amarillo hops. Our Brewers knew from the first batch that this one was a Keeper. Keeper’s Lager goes well with seafood: grilled whiting and flathead, salt and pepper calamari.
